{"type": "article", "id": 8992, "title": "芝士火锅凳", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-29T07:33:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234955jSTWb3PmwA7XazLC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本设计师 Satsuki Ohata 受火锅制作流程的启发，设计了这一款“好吃”的火锅凳。它的制作流程是：将高吸水海绵浸入到液体中，制成带色PVC，热风风干后凝固成固体方块，看上去就像巨型的奶酪。这款作品在米兰设计周的 Salone Satellite 展览上进行了展出。这里有 Satsuki Ohata 的个人主页，他有许多奇思妙想的设计，可以<a href=\"http://satsuki.co/product.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里进去查看</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523495013uolm96vernAkIp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234951r3i2RsyBxtUl9Ymq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234951WG6VUwuHsJTEKtfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234952SZGdIjJERQtglb7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234952rpVSnGe190NlETtK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234953a14MHjGD6SJFBT9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234953cNwFfkYUm6pXqHbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349533JvLl1U6WaXF5wHj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}